languages.text: {n}Группа поджарых молодых людей обступает вас со всех сторон. Испуганные взгляды незнакомцев мечутся между вами, Каллигосом, жрецом и седовласой старицей, сделавшей шаг вперед. В отличие от остальных кожа женщины чиста от нательных орнаментов, и лишь на ее морщинистом лбу парит выжженный двуглавый орел.{/n}

languages.text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Un grupo de hombres jóvenes y esbeltos te rodea. Su mirada se pasea nerviosamente de ti a Calligos, al sacerdote y a la anciana canosa que se ha adelantado. A diferencia de los demás, su piel está totalmente desprovista de adornos, a excepción del símbolo del águila bicéfala que tiene grabada a fuego en su arrugada frente.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Un grupo de hombres jóvenes y esbeltos te han rodeado. Su mirada se pasea nerviosamente de ti a Calligos, luego al sacerdote y de él a la anciana sacerdotisa de cabellos canos que se ha adelantado para dirigirse a ti. A diferencia de los demás, su piel está totalmente desprovista de adornos, a excepción del símbolo del águila bicéfala con las alas extendidas que tiene grabada a fuego en su arrugada frente.{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Civil_Overlord

languages.text: {n}一群瘦削的年轻人将你们团团围住，一位白发苍苍的老妇人从人群中走了出来。那些年轻人焦虑的目光在不断在你、卡里戈斯与老妇人之间游移。那位老妇人与其他人不同，她的皮肤上没有任何多余的身体彩绘，只有布满皱纹的额头上着双头鹰的印记。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}一群瘦削的年轻人将你们团团围住，一位白发苍苍的女祭司从人群中走了出来。那些年轻人焦虑的目光在不断在你、卡里戈斯与女祭司之间游移。那位女祭司与其他人不同，她的皮肤上没有任何多余的身体彩绘，只有布满皱纹的额头上着双头鹰的印记。{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Civil_Overlord

languages.text: {n}Un groupe de jeunes gens élancés dardent leurs regards anxieux entre vous, Calligos, le prêtre et la vieille prêtresse aux cheveux blancs qui s'avance vers vous. Contrairement aux autres, elle ne porte aucune ornementation, à l'exception d'une marque en forme d'aigle à deux têtes sur son front ridé.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Un groupe de jeunes hommes sveltes vous encercle. Ils dardent leurs regards anxieux entre vous, Calligos, le prêtre et la vieille prêtresse aux cheveux blancs qui s'avance vers vous. Contrairement aux autres, elle ne porte aucune ornementation corporelle, à l'exception d'une marque en forme d'aigle à deux têtes sur son front ridé.{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Civil_Overlord

languages.text: {n}痩せこけた若者たちがあなたの周りを取り囲む。彼らの不安げな視線が、あなたと、カリゴス、司祭、そして前に出てきた白髪頭の老司祭の間を飛び交っている。他の者たちと違って、彼女の肌には、しわにまみれたの額に焼きつけられた双頭の鷲の烙印を除いて、体の装飾品はまったくない。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}痩せこけた若者たちがあなたの周りを取り囲んでいる。彼らの不安げな視線が、あなたと、カリゴス、司祭、前に出てきた白髪頭の老司祭の間を飛び交っている。他の者たちと違って、彼女の肌には、しわにまみれたの額に焼きつけられた双頭の鷲の烙印を除いて、体の装飾品はまったくない。{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Civil_Overlord

languages.text: {n}Eine Gruppe drahtiger junger Leute umgibt dich. Ihre nervösen Blicke springen zwischen dir, Calligos, dem Priester und der grauhaarigen Ältesten hin und her, die vorgetreten ist. Im Gegensatz zu den anderen ist ihre Haut vollkommen frei von jeder Verzierung, abgesehen von dem Brandmal eines zweiköpfigen Adlers auf ihrer faltigen Stirn.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}A group of lean young people surrounds you, shooting anxious glances between you, Calligos, the priest, and the grey-headed elder who has stepped forward. Unlike the rest, her skin is completely free of decoration, save for the two-headed eagle branded on her wrinkled forehead.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Eine Gruppe drahtiger junger Männer hat dich umkreist. Ihre nervösen Blicke springen zwischen dir, Calligos, dem Priester und der grauhaarigen alten Priesterin hin und her, die vorgetreten ist. Im Gegensatz zu anderen ist ihre Haut vollkommen frei von Körperschmuck, abgesehen von dem Brandmal eines zweiköpfigen Adlers auf ihrer faltigen Stirn.{/n}
traits.speaker: Quetza-al_Civil_Overlord

languages.text: {n}Çelimsiz görünen bir grup genç, gergin bakışlarını bir sana, bir Calligos'a, bir rahibe ve bir de öne çıkan ihtiyara çevirip duruyor. Geri kalanların aksine ihtiyarın cildi, buruş buruş olmuş alnına damgalanan çift başlı kartal dışında tek bir süsleme dahi barındırmıyor.{/n}
